descriptionHTML:
Sushi Watch Face is new designed for Moto 360 and other smart watch (Android Wear).

★ 3 kawaii style watch face on day and will notice you the food time ★

100% compatible with LG G Watch R and LG Watch Urbane
Compatible with Moto 360, LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, Samsung Gear Live, ASUS ZenWatch, Sony SmartWach 2, Huawei smart watch and basically every watch using android wear round and square shape.


Note:
Sushi Watch Face does NOT work on Samsung Gear and Smart watches using other operating systems.

Features:
✔ Date
✔ Analog style
✔ 3 in one of watch face
✔ Alert when time to food and auto change watch face
✔ DIM mode display with Moon phases icon
✔ Round and square shape suppoted


Settings:
✔ Show date on/off
✔ Custom color of each watch face
✔ Set time to alert for Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner


INSTALLATION:
- After installing the app on your phone, then you will see Sushi watch face in the app "Android Wear".
- Please activate it from your Smart watch (Moto 360 or LG G Watch R) by Long press on the clock then select the Sushi watch face.

Please Note
* IF you don't want to get notice about new watch face and new apps please deselect "Notification for new watch face, apps"
